    <refsection id="Description_MMR_IdealGearGen">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            This block is an ideal gear. With this one, it is possible to choose if frame is fixed.
            In this case, the block has the same behaviour as <link linkend="MMR_IdealGear0">MMR_IdealGear0</link>.
            But if the frame is not fixed, the block is equivalent to <link linkend="MMR_IdealGear">MMR_IdealGear</link>,
            where bearings are taken into account.
        </para>
    </refsection>
